#gold.ts <- ts(gold[,2], start=c(2005, 02, 04), frequency=365.25)

# set gold as a xts object (for plots with dates)
gold.xts <- xts(gold, order.by=as.POSIXct(gold$Date), frequency=365)

# set gold as a time series object
gold.ts <- ts(gold$Value)

Original time series

layout(matrix(c(1,1,2,3), 2, 2, byrow = TRUE))
plot(gold.ts, main="gold.ts")
acf(gold.ts, lag.max = 30)
pacf(gold.ts, lag.max=30)

First differences

layout(matrix(c(1,1,2,3), 2, 2, byrow = TRUE))
plot(diff(gold.ts), main="diff(gold.ts)")
acf(diff(gold.ts), lag.max = 30)
pacf(diff(gold.ts), lag.max=30)

Differences of the log

layout(matrix(c(1,1,2,3), 2, 2, byrow = TRUE))

pacf(diff(log(gold.ts)), lag.max=30)
